    "description": "LastRo is a top-down shooter roguelike where you play robot, which mission is to clear up a lot of floors against different types of enemies and Bosses.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Upgrade Your Weapons / Robot </h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294330/extras/4579365e59bac9ce4e0fd240d49b8d85.poster.avif?t=1702292515\" width=570 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294330/extras/4579365e59bac9ce4e0fd240d49b8d85.webm?t=1702292515\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294330/extras/4579365e59bac9ce4e0fd240d49b8d85.mp4?t=1702292515\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Upgrade and evolve during each run<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Your eneimes also evolving</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294330/extras/8dff1426225ecbf17c2f3e2652cc892f.poster.avif?t=1702292515\" width=570 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294330/extras/8dff1426225ecbf17c2f3e2652cc892f.webm?t=1702292515\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294330/extras/8dff1426225ecbf17c2f3e2652cc892f.mp4?t=1702292515\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Enemies become stronger with difficulty and during the game.<br>You can choose which way and how much stronger they become.<br>Stronger enemies -&gt; more rewards<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Win or Die (Probably)</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unlock new features / upgrades / characters / weapons </h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294330/extras/2eae1b81ba14eb94202d1da5cab0cc2d.poster.avif?t=1702292515\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294330/extras/2eae1b81ba14eb94202d1da5cab0cc2d.webm?t=1702292515\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294330/extras/2eae1b81ba14eb94202d1da5cab0cc2d.mp4?t=1702292515\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >And Try again (or proceed to next difficulty)</h2><br>This game is completely free (no ads, no transactions). I'm not earning money from it (only spending tbh)<br>My point is to get as many players and reviews as possible. I appriciate any help with that.<br>I also feel that this game still lack much things: story, roguelike elements like path choosing, variety, balance, and so on...<br>But its good to go prototype<br>If you wish to support me go to any of socials<br>",
